  <steps>
    <step order="1">Locate the three request DTO files. `SemanticSearchRequest.cs` is at `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Models/Ai/SemanticSearch/`. Find `RagSearchRequest.cs` and `RecordSearchRequest.cs` under `Models/Ai/` (exact subfolder discovered during the task).</step>
